-- Swiss Central Bank Forecasts $5.15 Billion First-Half Loss on Currencies
-- Matthias Wabl
-- 2010-07-21T05:29:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-21/swiss-central-bank-forecasts-5-15-billion-first-half-loss-on-currencies.html

          
          
             The Swiss National Bank expects a
first-half loss of about 4 billion francs, it said in an e-
mailed statement today. Exchange rate losses amounted to more
than 14 billion francs, it said.  
          
          


  


        